data.description: A Must See! This stunning 5 bedroom Victorian home offers a perfect blend of classic charm and modern convenience. Situated on almost 2 acres of land, this property boasts many features. Upon entering you will be greeted with two living areas, a formal dining room, perfect for entertaining. The kitchen is complete with a butlers pantry for additional storage and preparation space. The original hardwood floors throughout the home add a touch of warmth and character, while the crown molding adds a touch of elegance. The spacious bedrooms are complemented by walk-in closets. The partial finished basement offers additional living space, perfect for a home office, playroom or gym. Outside you will find a charming gazebo, perfect for relaxing and enjoying the landscaping that surrounds the property. The covered porch is the ideal spot to unwind and enjoy the peacefulness of the surroundings. This Victorian home embodies the timeless beauty and sophistication of a bygone era, while offering all the modern comforts and amenities that make it a great place to call home.
